MATERIALS USED : VARIOUS VALUES OF GRAPHITE PENCILS, DRAWING PAPER, KNEADER ERASER, MECHANICHAL PENCIL, PROPORTIONAL DIVIDER, ERASER AND FIXATIVE FOR LONG LIFE OF ARTWORK.

METHOD : PENCILS ON DRAWING PAPER.

PACKAGE WEIGHT (APPROX) : 1 KG

PACKING : IN A TUBE OR WITH HARD BOARDS ON BOTH SIDES.

RETURN AND REFUND POLICY:

Any discrepancy or any issue on quality, buyer may please be intimated to us within 7 days from the receipt of artwork. Refund or a replacement will be provided in due course. In case of overseas buyer, inward and outward shipping charges are to be borne by them.

SHIPPING INFO:

Generally, all shipments are done through courier services . Price quoted are inclusive of shipment charges for India and for outside India, it is extra as per the prevailing rates.
